raw_data.title: IT Data Quality Analyst
raw_data.description: IT Data Quality Management. Oversee a small team focused on supporting information gathering, data quality, data consolidation, data extraction methods along with upload management, customized reporting and process methodology as required by the Client set in the projects Statement of Work.  Knowledge of data quality processes and ability to help review and correct data from systems that utilize Optical Character Recognition (OCR).  Comp TIA A+ IT certification, data analysis or equivalent experience preferred.

raw_data.title: Program Manager
raw_data.description: Responsible for planning and managing medium-to-large sized technology related projects and cross-functional strategic initiatives of moderate-to-high complexity. Responsible for all stages of the project life cycle including: (1)initiating, (2)planning, (3)executing, (4)monitoring / controlling, (5)closing (6) Report writing. Manage scope changes and keeping project on task and within budget.

raw_data.title: Senior Subject Matter Expert
raw_data.description: Recognized for technical knowledge and judgment in a technical field with proficiency in relevant principles and practices as required for technically complex assignments. Develops solutions to difficult problems. Generates concepts as evidenced by product or process improvement. Uses tools to integrate requirements and solve technical problems. Utilizes tools, techniques, processes and/or facilities such as state-of-the-art solutions. Leads engineering team activities in a specialized technology subject area. Contributes to the technical planning process and provides technical guidance. General experience includes enterprise level systems engineering, analysis, and design.

raw_data.title: Systems Engineer IV
raw_data.description: Responsible for technical aspects of the implementation of content management solutions. These include: (1) Technical Design, (2) Determination of current Network Infrastructure Capabilities, (3) Hardware Recommendations, (4) System analysis, (5) Installation of software, (6) Integration services (6) Testing of installed software (7)  Workflow development (8) Forms design (9)Training on installed software, (10) Ongoing Support of installed software.  To perform these functions the individual should be certified by the software manufacturers.
